---
alwaysApply: true
---

- After a relevant (non-trivial) change, always check the current version of the app in the README.md
  - check `docs/ChangeLog.md` and if the last changelog matches the same in the README.MD, then bump the changelog version by `+0.01 (only in the changelog) and add a short changelog note for that new version.
  - if in `docs/ChangeLog.md` the version is higher that the one in README>MD, then don't bump, just keep adding notes to the last version number.
  los changelogs siempre van en castellano!


